      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
         <p>The papers of Edmund Bergler (1899-1962) span the years 1943-1978 and
		  consist largely of Berglerâ€™s letters to Mrs. Walter Charak between 1945 and
		  1950 in which he discussed his writings as well as hers. Also included are
		  reprints of articles on psychiatric and psychoanalytic subjects published by
		  Bergler between 1943 and 1948. </p>
      </scopecontent>
